ore emergency contacts.\n\n## 3. Enable **Wireless Emergency Alerts (WEA)** on your phone\n- These alerts (e.g., Amber Alerts, severe weather) are automatically sent to all compatible smartphones.\n- Ensure your device’s emergency alert settings are turned **ON** in the system settings.\n\n### Summary of Steps\n1. Call one of the Notify NYC numbers above to register for phone alerts.\n2. Optionally, download the Ready NYC app for richer notifications and preparedness tools.\n3. Verify that your phone’s WEA settings are enabled to receive automatic alerts.\n\nBy following these three actions, you will receive NYC emergency alerts via phone calls, text messages, the Ready NYC app, and automatic wireless alerts.\n\n</content>', include_extracted_content_only_once=True, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Successfully replaced all occurrences of "- [ ] Summarize steps for the user" with "- [x] Summarize steps for the user" in file todo.md', extracted_content='Successfully replaced all occurrences of "- [ ] Summarize steps for the user" with "- [x] Summarize steps for the user" in file todo.md', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=False, success=None, error=None, attachments=None, long_term_memory='Successfully replaced all occurrences of "- [ ] Review and finalize answer" with "- [x] Review and finalize answer" in file todo.md', extracted_content='Successfully replaced all occurrences of "- [ ] Review and finalize answer" with "- [x] Review and finalize answer" in file todo.md', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False), ActionResult(is_done=True, success=True, error=None, attachments=['/var/folders/t8/7vk5qmnd04z9fn7y0q8bynyh0000gn/T/browser_use_agent_068e5b98-d086-721b-8000-aa184a6d205b_1759885709/browseruse_agent_data/results.md'], long_term_memory='Task completed: 