lly sent to all compatible smartphones.\n- Ensure your device’s emergency alert settings are turned **ON** in the system settings.\n\n### Summary of Steps\n1. Call one of the Notify NYC numbers above to register for phone alerts.\n2. Optionally, download the Ready NYC app for richer notifications and preparedness tools.\n3. Verify that your phone’s WEA settings are enabled to receive automatic alerts.\n\nBy following these three actions, you will receive NYC emergency alerts via phone calls, text messages, the Ready NYC app, and automatic wireless alerts.\n', include_extracted_content_only_once=False, metadata=None, include_in_memory=False)], all_model_outputs=[{'go_to_url': {'url': 'https://www.nyc.gov', 'new_tab': False}, 'interacted_element': None}, {'click_element_by_index': {'index': 7}, 'interacted_element': DOMInteractedElement(node_id=184, backend_node_id=1175, frame_id=None, node_type=<NodeType.ELEMENT_NODE: 1>, node_value='', node_name='BUTTON', attributes={'id': 'global-search-button', 'class': 'cmp-button', 'data-ck': 'xx57dc5d21-53d5-4b01-a6f4-a080902abc4c', 'data-oid': 'cityofnewyorkproduction1oub1837a', 'aria-controls': 'global-search-modal', 'data-open-modal': ''}, bounds=DOMRect(x=929.15625, y=52.1875, width=128.015625, height=44.0), x_path='html/body/div[2]/div/header/div/div/div/div[2]/div/div/div[3]/button', element_hash=4407204861276460702)}, {'write_file': {'file_name': 'todo.md', 'content': '# NYC Emergency Alerts Task\n\n## Goal: Provide instructions on how to receive NYC emergency alerts on a phone using only nyc.gov\n\n## Tasks:\n- [ ] Search for "emergency alerts phone" on nyc.gov\n- [ ] Identify the official NYC emergency alerts page\n- [ ] Determine available phone alert methods (SMS, app, etc.)\n- [ ] Summarize steps for the user\n- [ ] Review and finalize answer', 'append': False, 'trailing_newline': True, 'leading_newline': False}, 'interacted_element': None}, {'input_text': {'index': 3, 'text': 'emergency alerts phone', 'clear_existi